<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<title>消费排行</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/swiper-3.3.1.min.css"/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reset.css"/>
		<link href='http://cdn.webfont.youziku.com/webfonts/nomal/111819/46865/5ad70578f629d91254ccbd45.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/consumer-rank.css"/>
		<script src="js/jquery-2.2.4.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<script src="js/swiper-3.3.1.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<script src="js/rem.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="rank-wrap">
			<img class="xf-big-bg" src="img/xfbottom.png"/>
			<div class="rank-banner">
				<img class="rank-banner-img" src="img/xfbanner.png"/>
			</div>
			<div class="rank-content">
				<p class="rank-content-tit"><img src="img/left1.png"/>&nbsp;消费实时排行&nbsp; <img src="img/right1.png"/></p>
				<div class="rank-table-wrap">
					<table class="rank-table" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
						<tr><th>排名</th><th>会员名称</th><th>消费金额(元)</th></tr>
						<tr><td>1</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>2</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>3</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>4</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>5</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>6</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>7</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>8</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>9</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
						<tr><td>10</td><td>1234****910</td><td>5678910</td></tr>
					</table>
				</div>
				<p class="rank-content-tit"><img src="img/left1.png"/>&nbsp;奖项设置说明&nbsp; <img src="img/right1.png"/></p>
				<div class="words-five-card rank-award-set swiper-container">
					<div class="rank-award-wrap swiper-wrapper">
						<div class="swiper-slide rank-award">
							<p class="rank-award-tit">The first prize</p>
							<p class="rank-award-tit2"><span></span>&nbsp;一等奖&nbsp;<span></span></p>
							<p class="rank-award-tit3">创维电视（共1名）</p>
							<img class="rank-prize" src="img/prize1.png"/>
						</div>
						<div class="swiper-slide rank-award">
							<p class="rank-award-tit">The second prize</p>
							<p class="rank-award-tit2"><span></span>&nbsp;二等奖&nbsp;<span></span></p>
							<p class="rank-award-tit3">创意椅子（共2名）</p>
							<img class="rank-prize" src="img/prize2.png"/>
						</div>
						<div class="swiper-slide rank-award">
							<p class="rank-award-tit">The third prize</p>
							<p class="rank-award-tit2"><span></span>&nbsp;三等奖&nbsp;<span></span></p>
							<p class="rank-award-tit3">奖蔷薇刀（共3名）</p>
							<img class="rank-prize" src="img/prize3.png"/>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="rank-content-tit"><img src="img/left1.png"/>&nbsp;活动规则&nbsp; <img src="img/right1.png"/></p>
				<div class="rank-ruls">
					<p>1.活动期间，根据商城消费实时排行榜，消费前十名根据消费金额高低，分为一等奖、二等奖、三等奖，均可以获得不同礼品。</p>
					<p>2.活动期间，如商品未出现质量问题，不接受任何形式退换货。</p>
					<p>3.活动期间，如出现特殊退换货情况，将核销相应消费金额。</p>
					<p>4.消费排行均以活动期间支付完成订单为最终依据，计入消费总金额。</p>
					<p>5.如出现恶意作弊行为光明行商城有权利视情况而定，决定是否收回已发放的奖品。 </p>
					<p>6.活动奖品以实物为准。 </p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			var mySwiper = new Swiper('.swiper-container',{
				effect : 'coverflow',
				slidesPerView: 1.5,
				centeredSlides: true,
				loop:true,
				coverflow: {
				            rotate: 0,
				            stretch: 10,
				            depth: 30,
				            modifier: -4,
				            slideShadows : false
				        }
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
